<h2>About</h2>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-6">
        <p>Slot Cars Go! is a race management system for the Scalextric<sup>&reg;</sup> Digital 6-Car Powerbase system by Hornby Ltd.</p>
        <p>
            Inspired by the <a href="http://ssdc.jackaments.com/">Scalextric Sport Digital Console</a> system, Slot Cars Go! is the first
            client-server solution for the Scalextric 6-Car Powerbase that allows players to view their race sessions on the web (AFAIK).
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-6">
        <img src="~/Content/Images/c7042-advanced-6-car-powerbase-box.jpg"/>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-6">
        <img src="~/Content/Images/RaceTypeSelect.png" />
