    <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-6">
        <p>The Slot Cars Go! race management client is available for any device running Windows 10 - from a PC, laptop to a Raspberry Pi!</p>
        <p>Requirements:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Scalextric<sup>&reg;</sup> <a href="https://www.scalextric.com/uk-en/scalextric-digital-advanced-6-car-powerbase.html">Digital 6-Car Powerbase</a></li>
            <li>Custom USB to C7042 APB Cable from <a href="http://www.rikorocket.co.uk/products/usb-to-c7042-apb/">RikoRocket</a></li>
            <li>Any device running Windows 10:</li>
            <ol>
                <li>PC on Windows 10</li>
                <li>Laptop on Windows 10</li>
                <li>Raspberry Pi on Windows 10 IoT Core</li>
            <ol/>
            <li>The SlotCarsGo! Universal Windows Application</li>
            <li>An internet connection</li>
            <li>A free account here at <a href="https://slotcarsgo.timtyler.co.uk">Slot Cars Go!</a></li>
            </ol>
        </ol>
    </div>
</div>
